														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2470317">
									

<p>Glad that this sees the light of day since the days where I secretly browse through the Sarkic Hub for more information on Sarkicism. I have to ask: the Sarkic organisms are not classified as SCPs, even though they could be.</p>
<p>Or maybe it is a glossary to better classify them for the future.</p>
<p>EDIT: If someone does a Sarkic SCP/Tale/GoI format, will it be added to the hub?</p>

