			<div class="content" id="post-content-2471152">
									

<p>God. Damn.</p>
<p>This is really impressive, Meta. Writing this took a lot of knowledge about biology, world history, linguistics, religious history&#8230; And you still managed to wrap it all up with a Cronenberg joke at the end.</p>
<p>Damned good work. I seriously can't get over the amount of research you must have had to do to make all of this fit together so nicely. I feel like I have an obligation to suggest that you might have an unhealthy obsession, but then I realize that if you get help, I won't get to enjoy your writing anymore.</p>
<p>Carry on, then.</p>

